label: SDTM Variable ID
definition: The unique SDTM code for a class in this model.

label: SDTM domain code
definition: The two letter code for the SDTM domain.

label: SDTM domain name
definition: The full name of the SDTM domain.

label: SDTM label
definition: The label used by SDTM. Sometimes does not match the semantics of the class.
